name: Greeata
Lore: 'Rodian musician. In addition to her singing talents, she plays kloo horn. Befriended Sy Snootles on the luxury liner Kuari Princess.',
Text: 'Other Rodians deploy -1 to same site. Once during each of your control phases, may use 1 Force to take any Rodian into hand from Reserve Deck- reshuffle. While at Audience Chamber, all your other musicians are deploy -1 and forfeit +3.',
